data.description: Prime location in Hoschton! This spacious 5-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home boasts a welcoming extended entry foyer leading to a cozy great room with a fireplace, perfect for gathering with loved ones. The great room flows seamlessly into an expansive kitchen featuring an oversized center work island with bar stool seating and a convenient walk-in pantry. Upstairs, you'll find the luxurious master bedroom complete with a sizable walk-in closet, double vanity, separate garden tub, and enclosed shower for ultimate relaxation. Four additional generously-sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms provide ample space for family and guests. For added convenience, the laundry room is conveniently located upstairs. Natural light fills every corner of this inviting home, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step outside to discover a fabulous fenced backyard and extended patio featuring an outdoor fireplace, ideal for enjoying outdoor gatherings and creating lasting memories. This home is situated in a community with sidewalk access to the newly developed Jackson County public school system, offering convenience and peace of mind. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this wonderful property your new home!
